<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.8.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div id="banner" class="w-100">
            <img style="height:200px; width: 100%" src="https://metropole.rennes.fr/sites/default/files/styles/cover_1440_500/public/img-thematique/3_Habitat2Jeremias%20Gonzalez.jpg?itok=G8HJylOE" class="img-fluid" alt="...">
        </div>
        <div id="description_page" class="w-100">
            <h1 class="display-1 text-center">Titre de la page</h1>
            <div id="description">
                <p class="text-sm-left">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras semper commodo felis, ut faucibus enim. In feugiat sapien erat, in dapibus mauris lobortis in. Pellentesque porttitor vel elit nec euismod. Suspendisse potenti. Aliquam pellentesque massa ut metus semper placerat. Cras auctor ipsum tempor enim convallis, a dignissim est vestibulum. Sed sed tempor augue. Nulla a feugiat sem. Morbi ultricies luctus consequat. Nulla tempus, tellus id convallis finibus, purus lacus euismod ligula, eget euismod mauris nulla ac orci. Proin ut pulvinar diam. Donec tortor lectus, placerat nec ante quis, efficitur sagittis lectus. Integer urna velit, auctor eu pretium quis, pellentesque at purus. Curabitur ullamcorper dictum hendrerit. Phasellus a nunc sit amet orci dignissim consectetur.
                    Lien vers l’API : </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="myAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h1 class="display-6 text-left p-3" id="">
                    API 3D
                </h1>
                <div id="" class="accordion-collapse">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col col-1 card-body justify-content-center">
                            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Etiam rutrum, ipsum at semper rutrum, nisl dui tempus libero, eget eleifend sem sapien non dolor. Class aptent taciti sociosqu ad litora torquent per conubia nostra, per inceptos himenaeos. Aenean placerat venenatis neque, cursus vehicula ipsum blandit non. Vestibulum sagittis quam vel neque congue ultrices. Nam faucibus, mauris id rutrum accumsan, velit dui posuere diam, cursus mattis eros metus a sem. Praesent quis nibh mollis, scelerisque nunc in, varius elit. Nulla elit tortor, faucibus nec leo id, eleifend tristique leo. Praesent feugiat aliquet ligula, et scelerisque purus commodo at. Quisque ullamcorper nibh mauris, vitae tempor risus accumsan id.</p>
                            <p>Donec imperdiet ante sit amet mattis bibendum. Etiam placerat fringilla dui a fermentum. Aliquam eleifend, tortor at luctus dictum, lorem lectus efficitur nulla, non accumsan tellus est sed leo. Duis vel lacinia libero. Curabitur non iaculis turpis. Sed vitae mauris finibus, sollicitudin libero non, laoreet nibh. Morbi hendrerit ut sem vitae dictum. Nullam vel sagittis dui. In consectetur porta elit, vitae commodo turpis egestas lobortis. Fusce tempus dui eu neque vulputate, at venenatis purus sollicitudin.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
                <% for(var i=0; i < metadata.length; i++) { %>
                   <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading<%= i %>">
                        <button type="button" class="accordion-button collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse<%= i %>"><i class=" p-3 bi bi-hdd-fill"></i><%= metadata[i].title %></button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapse<%= i %>" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#myAccordion">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col col-1 card-body justify-content-center">
                                <p class="h3">Description</p>
                                <%= metadata[i].abstract %>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col col-3">
                                <p class="h3 text-center">Aperçu</p>
                                <div class="ng-scope"> <img data-gn-img-modal="img" class="gn-img-thumbnail img-thumbnail" alt="" data-ng-src="<%= metadata[i].apercu %>" src="<%= metadata[i].apercu %>">
                                    <div class="gn-img-thumbnail-caption ng-binding ng-hide" data-ng-show="img.label"> </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col col-12">
                                <p class="h3">Téléchargements et liens</p>
                                <div class="row list-group-item mt-3">
                                    <div class="col" style="height: 40px;"> 
                                        <i class="bi bi-globe"></i> 
                                        <span class="h5"><%= metadata[i].title %></span> 
                                        <a href="/files/<%= metadata[i].file %>" class="float-end btn btn-light">
                                            Télécharger
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row mt-4">
                            <div class="col col-8">
                                <p class="h3">À propos de cette ressource</p>
                                <table class="table table-striped">
                                    <tbody> 
                                        <tr class="ng-scope">
                                            <th data-translate="" class="ng-scope">Date de révision</th>
                                            <td><%= metadata[i].date_revision %></td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr class="ng-scope">
                                            <th data-translate="" class="ng-scope">Licence</th>
                                            <td><%= metadata[i].licence %></td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col col-4">
                                <p class="h3">Contact</p>
                                <div class="gn-contact flex-row ng-scope">
                                    <div class="flex-noshrink"> <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i> </div>
                                    <div class="flex-spacer"></div> <address>
                                        <div class="ng-scope">
                                            <ul>
                                                <li class="ng-binding ng-scope"> Point de contact :<br />
                                                    <div> <strong class="ng-binding"><%= metadata[i].contact.name %></strong> </div>
                                                    <%= metadata[i].contact.adresse.rue %> <%= metadata[i].contact.adresse.codepostal %> - <%= metadata[i].contact.adresse.ville %> 
                                                    <br /><span class="ng-scope"><span class="ng-scope"> <i class="bi bi-envelope-fill"></i> <a href="mailto:<%= metadata[i].contact.email %>"><%= metadata[i].contact.email %></a><br />
                                                            <i class="bi bi-telephone-fill"></i> <%= metadata[i].contact.phone %></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </address>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="footer mt-auto py-3 bg-light">
	  <div class="container">
	    <span class="text-muted">Mentions légales</span>
	  </div>
	</footer>
</body>

</html>